item.title: Code for barrows set or drag?
item.dc:creator: @MoparScape_Questions MoparScape Questions
item.description:
@MoparScape_Questions wrote:

Just open MoparScape webclient , go to
File–>Help–>Item I.D’s , and search for it there.

There will be two I.D.'s for each item. First one is item itself as one, second is item noted. So if you want more than one item, use the its second ID.
